<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.7">
<l>vaiya mellā muṭaṉvaṇaṅkavaṇaṅkā maṉṉa ṉāyttōṉṟi</l>
<l>veyya cīṟṟak kaṭiyilaṅkai kuṭikoṇ ṭōṭa veñcamattu</l>
<l>ceyta vempōr namparaṉaic ceḻuntaṇ kāṉal maṇanāṟum</l>
<l>kaitai vēlik kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our supreme lord who, having appeared as a king who was dishonored</l>
<l>As, at the same time, all the world honored him,</l>
<l rend="indent">did heated combat in heated battle,</l>
<l>So that [those of] hot, angry, guarded Laṅkā fled, taking their families,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself in Kaṇṇapuram, with screwpine hedges</l>
<l rend="indent">that waft fragrance in the cool, verdant groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
